Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:52.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has \Never fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:13.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:17.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the \NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:35.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and were drawn into a climactic \Nbattle on Punk Hazard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhich ended with Caesar's capture.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, they left the island\Nalong with their pirate ally -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the Warlord - Law. However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law is different but Straw Hat \Nis just an ordinary pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go, you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were talking on the \NTransponder Snail earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His underground alias is Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Joker's most important \Nbusiness partner now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the Four Emperor -\NKaido, the King of the Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way to find \Nout who knows what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Law, Straw \NHat, and you soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you step aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Intense!\NAokiji vs. Doflamingo!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the former admiral - Aokiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he disappeared \Nafter Akainu beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank god-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't get frozen to the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in fighting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can't silence that guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to change my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...current status, Kuzan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reputation is sullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, treat him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a difference between\Nthe look of an ordinary vagabond
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that of a determined man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that the World \NGovernment was almighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I can do\Nwithout belonging to the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I can see now\Nbecause I'm not part of the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dead for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was fated to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have something to do with\Nthe underground community now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The former admiral has \Nsomething to do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're done with the \Ntreatment, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still me, Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have no qualms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you guys should \Nkeep an eye on Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Warlord and the \Nking of Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an unusual pirate in many ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but not like the Snake Princess of the Kuja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Sakazuki and get the \Nadmirals into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst-case scenario,\Nthings could go very wrong, very quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it would become the most \Nserious matter Sakazuki faced
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since taking over Navy HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to keep it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot. Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we'll keep it \N{\i1}secret{\i0} that we saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His underground alias is Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Joker's most important \Nbusiness partner now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the Four Emperor -\NKaido, the King of the Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our target.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! K-Kaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a dragon here?!\NWhere did Momonosuke go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This dragon is Momonosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido of the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to take him down,\Nwe have to weaken his forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido is buying a large amount \Nof fruit from Joker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Zoan-type, man-made \NDevil Fruit - SMILE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Man-made?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If such a thing exists,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of Devil Fruit \Neaters will keep multiplying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's man-made, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nit seems like there are some risks involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in fact, Kaido has \Nmore than 500 Devil Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,eaters in his pirate group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who doesn't wanna do this?! I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't!\N--I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Devil Fruit eaters \Nwon't multiply anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you making a substance\Nfor the man-made Devil Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cool! SAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't praise him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that hard to make the SAD thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just put Vegapunk's discovery \Nof "lineage factor" into practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Vegapunk {\i1}is{\i0} the smart one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you bastards!\NCan you fools even make it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever call us "fools"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker is finished.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go onto the next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a factory manufacturing SMILEs\Nsomewhere on Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just find it and destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Kaido's forces won't strengthen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he's a professional \Nbusinessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressrosa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that where you wanna go, Kin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're keeping one of \Nmy comrades prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, something is falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those clouds?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna start raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not rain, it's hail (arare).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh (ara).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NIs there something to those clouds?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, prepare for Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, take the helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta furl the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what those clouds are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard aport! Coup de \NBurst toward 9 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Head for an area with no clouds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't! No, no, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, did you like it?\NDon't you think this ship is cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is impossible\Nfor the Thousand Sunny that I built!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}super{\i0}, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is {\i1}super{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo-{\i1}chan{\i0}, do you wanna \Nlook around the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Alright, you may!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you turn back to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already late! No one has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! I didn't see anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think they \Ncan still find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people are looking for us?!\NTens of thousands?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop worrying\Nsince I heard you blackmailed Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, neither, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin gave us armor and some helmets.\NJust let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resign from the Warlords\Nor fight one of the Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can choose between those options.\NHe'll just come to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Fight me squarely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's a long story!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cut it out!\N--Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! It's dangerous \Nto fight on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you playing samurai?!\NFight, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed of yourself!\NThe whole country was left heartbroken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grave of the Wano Kingdom's hero,\Nleft plundered by a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have! You have \Nlegendary swordsman
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuma's great sword Shusui on your belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on! Fight, fight!\NJust cut him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants to eat a midnight snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pida{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what that is\Nbut if he cooked it, it should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke went to bed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking a bath with Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't taken a bath \Nfor days, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get all warmed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came at just the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NKin'emon-{\i1}san{\i0}, he needs a kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you dirty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking full advantage \Nof being a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cut off your top-knot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why did you gang up on a child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not what you think, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NMen are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared, beautiful princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful princess?!\NDon't be so honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a lovely boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sleep in our room, Momo-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll let him in the girls' \Nroom - the secret garden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:23:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? You found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
